title: VonZipper : Brand Video 2011
description: VonZipper is about lifestyle and personality. Our mission is to develop, design and deliver premium eyewear, goggles, soft goods and accessories to the alternative mindset through participation in the sideways subculture and a commitment to the individual. Everything we do is a reflection of relationships from employees and team riders, to our retailers and their customers. We bring smiles to faces and touch people with positive declarations of rebellion against the norm.
